{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 816433, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 169224, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "什么是更有意义的事呢？", "timestamp": 1609471449, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 816462, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 169224, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "就比较一下有多少东西是你从清华课程里学到的，有多少东西是从课程之外学到的吧，粗浅点说，自己学学编程，学学新的技能，也是好的", "timestamp": 1609471732, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 816524, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 169224, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 学到实实在在的知识（包括专业知识，别的科目的知识等等），社会工作等等吧", "timestamp": 1609472381, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 816548, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 169224, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "均绩4.0是跳跃，收益为无穷", "timestamp": 1609472885, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 816646, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 169224, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那GPA炸了保研不是只能去水平不行的老师那里", "timestamp": 1609474122, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 816716, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 169224, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 不是", "timestamp": 1609474756, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 818502, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 169224, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 真的吗", "timestamp": 1609496829, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 818507, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 169224, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 我当年保研，老师当场看我没出分的期末考了多少", "timestamp": 1609496852, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 818513, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 169224, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 而且老师对于GPA特别高的直接收了，但是给我博士名额前还额外考核了", "timestamp": 1609496912, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 169224, "reply": 9, "tag": null, "text": "如果你真的想当卷王，那另说。否则的话，其实还有一种不错的思路：自己喜欢的/感兴趣的课好好学，争取拿高分；不那么感兴趣的课，尽力学；对于真的没意义的屑课，与其把大量时间花在那上面，不如自己学点有价值的东西。\n\n**绩点不是大学学习的全部，均绩4.0的收益，可能真不如适当放低对成绩的要求，做点更有意义的事。**", "timestamp": 1609471278, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1609496912, "url": "", "vote": {}}}